works.description:
For those who liked the concept of the  
YikeBike electric mini-farthing, but couldn’t afford it owing to its hefty  
price of $3,795, the New Zealand-based company has now unveiled the new  
Fusion model that will cost you just $1,995 (if you can still afford it).  
It’s just like the original YikeBike folding electric bike, except for the  
fact that there is no carbon fiber this time.
